<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref864" name="_ftn864" title="" id="_ftn864"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[864]</span></span></a> “Israel’s Refusal to Grant Palestinian Refugees Right to Return has Fuelled Seven Decades of Suffering,” Amnesty International, press release, May 15, 2019, amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2019/05/israels-refusal-to-grant-palestinian-refugees-right-to-return-has-fuelled-seven-decades-of-suffering/ (accessed May 3, 2020).</p>&#13;
</div>&#13;
&#13;
<div id="ftn865">&#13;
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref865" name="_ftn865" title="" id="_ftn865"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[865]</span></span></a> Rome Statute, art 7(1)(h), art(7)(1)(k), art 8(2)(g), art 8(2)(h).</p>&#13;
</div>&#13;
&#13;
<div id="ftn866">&#13;
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref866" name="_ftn866" title="" id="_ftn866"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[866]</span></span></a> Human Rights Watch Policy on the Right of Return.</p>&#13;
